    <step order="4" name="Wire Write Path">In compression service or chat persistence path, vectorize each turn / summary + persist alongside metadata.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Wire Read Path">In `PlaybookChatContextProvider` memory composition step, call recall for top-K.</step>
